Package it.polimi.se2.clupapplication.model

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AuthenticationResponseDTO
    Data Transfer Object representing the authentication response information, which consists in a username and a redirect url to which users will be brought if the login process is successful.
    AuthTokenDTO
    Data Transfer Object representing the authentication token sent to the client, which consists in a string of mixed characters.
    LoginUserDTO
    Data Transfer Object representing the authentication information, which consists in a username and a password.
    SlotDTO
    Data Transfer Object representing the Slot information, which consists in a starting hour, a store capacity, a store id and a code of the specified day.
    StoreDTO
    Data Transfer Object representing the Store information.
    UserDTO
    Data Transfer Object representing the User object information, generally used during the sign up process.
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    Status
    This enum contains the status that a ticket can assume during its lifecycle.
